eedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104foi1665702608242.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/foi1665702608242.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/foi1665702608242.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"foi1665702608242\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the location where the online documentation is located. Applicable only for\n      HTML or <span class=\"ph filepath\">.hlp</span>.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"foi1665702608242__topic_d145382e1_d145383e1_d145384e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"foi1665702608242__p_d145385e1_d145386e1_d145387e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">HelpDir</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DirectoryPath</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"foi1665702608242__section_w3215ab1b5b3_w3216ab1b5_w3217ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"foi1665702608242__table_d17723e1_d17724e1_d17725e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceApsDir</var>/doc/help</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"otb1665703261079.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/otb1665703261079.html\" title=\"The [paths] section of the initialization file specifies the locations of the local working directory, help files, images, and JavaScript files generated during compilation.\">[paths]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"foi1665702608242__section_mvw_xrp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d502916e113\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"foi1665702608242__p_d145391e1_d145392e1_d145393e1\">This setting is only applicable if the following\n            conditions are met:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"foi1665702608242__ul_sr5_yrp_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"foi1665702608242__li_d50558e1_d50559e1_d50560e1\">Online help documentation is available in native\n               format, that is, as HTML files (if <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hhz1665703258861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hhz1665703258861.html\" title=\"For applications deployed on Windows, specifies whether the native online help is HTML-based or WinHelp.\">HtmlHelp</a> is True) or\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">.hlp</span> files. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"foi1665702608242__li_d50561e1_d50562e1_d50563e1\">Help is invoked in the application using the\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> ProcScript statement. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"foi1665702608242__li_d50564e1_d50565e1_d50566e1\">The [HELP] INI file section lists the help files\n               that can be called. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"foi1665702608242__note_prb_zrp_xvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The WinHelp (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.hlp</span>) format is\n            obsolete. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">HELPDIR</span> setting is not used to locate HTML Help\n               (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.chm</span>) files.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/igs1665702672514.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[help]</a><p>The [help] section of the initialization file specifies the files to be used when online help is requested by the help ProcScript statement from a Uniface application, or within displayed messages.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527598\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527598\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "HelpDir Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the location where the online documentation is located. Applicable only for HTML or .hlp . HelpDir = DirectoryPath Default value: UnifaceApsDir /doc/help File section: [paths] Description This setting is only applicable if the following conditions are met: Online help documentation is available in native format, that is, as HTML files (if HtmlHelp is True) or .hlp files. Help is invoked in the application using the help ProcScript statement. The [HELP] INI file section lists the help files that can be called. Note: The WinHelp ( .hlp ) format is obsolete. The HELPDIR setting is not used to locate HTML Help ( .chm ) files. Related Links [help] The [help] section of the initialization file specifies the files to be used when online help is requested by the help ProcScript statement from a Uniface application, or within displayed messages. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}